### ==========================================
### MÓDULO: CITAS MÉDICAS
### ==========================================

### 5. Agendar una Cita Médica (Paciente Juan)
POST https://localhost:7086/api/Citas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "pacienteId": 4,
  "fechaHora": "2026-04-15T10:30:00",
  "motivoConsulta": "Dolor de cabeza severo y fiebre"
}

### 10. Agendamos a otra paciente (María) - Mismo ID de paciente 1 por rapidez
POST https://localhost:7086/api/Citas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "pacienteId": 4,
  "fechaHora": "2026-04-16T12:00:00",
  "motivoConsulta": "Limpieza Dental"
}

### 6. Ver la agenda de la clínica
GET https://localhost:7086/api/Citas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. El Doctor termina la consulta de Juan Pérez (Cita ID 1) y le cobra $850.00
POST https://localhost:7086/api/Citas/1/completar
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "monto": 850.00
}

### 11. Terminamos la cita de María y le cobramos $500.00
POST https://localhost:7086/api/Citas/2/completar
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "monto": 500.00
}

### ==========================================
### MÓDULO: COBROS Y REPORTES
### ==========================================

### 8. La Recepcionista revisa quién falta de pagar hoy
GET https://localhost:7086/api/Cobros/pendientes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Juan Pérez paga en la terminal y Recepción registra el pago (Cobro ID 1)
POST https://localhost:7086/api/Cobros/1/pagar
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Recepción registra el pago de María (Cobro ID 2)
POST https://localhost:7086/api/Cobros/2/pagar
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. ¡EL REPORTE FINAL DE GERENCIA!
GET https://localhost:7086/api/Reportes/ingresos-acumulados
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}